{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820770/extras/\u043e\u0442\u0441\u0442\u0443\u043f-steam.png?t=1733168023\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820770/extras/Add-to-wishlist-steam-3.gif?t=1733168023\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820770/extras/\u043e\u0442\u0441\u0442\u0443\u043f-steam.png?t=1733168023\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820770/extras/Narrative.gif?t=1733168023\" />The essence of emptiness is a part of the human soul that grows as it commits cruel sinful acts. With an empty soul, a person loses their humanity, revealing their inner stench. Requests that previously seemed alien to morality become his own desires.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Responding to the call of the void is the easiest way to lose your humanity and your own appearance along with your soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820770/extras/\u043e\u0442\u0441\u0442\u0443\u043f-steam.png?t=1733168023\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2820770/extras/Info.gif?t=1733168023\" />Drawn Tale is a creepy adventure set in a 3D world with hand-drawn graphics. The story follows the trials of a boy named Mor who finds himself in a mysterious place called &quot;Purgatory.&quot; There, he will encounter dangerous monsters, cruel creatures, and his own demons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you'll find puzzles, drama, atmospheric music, dark humor, and a fair amount of cruelty, all set against the backdrop of beautiful hand-drawn visuals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://sha